General Information

A citrus splash of pure essential oils blended with warming Ginger to uplift and refresh your mind and body.

Warnings

STORE BELOW 30C. NOT TO BE TAKEN ORALLY. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN.

Ingredients

Orange, Grapefruit, Lemon, Lime, Lemongrass, Bergamot and Ginger

Directions

Add 6 drops to your vapouriser for an invigorating aroma. Application to skin may increase sensitivity to sunlight.
